%labels
    chmod 755 /home/user

    Author  "Generated by ChatGPT - Apptainer setup"

%help
    This container provides the initial filesystem state for the
    Apache log–analysis task.  The original access log is located at
    /home/user/logs/access.log; no solution artefacts are present.  The
    environment includes Python and pytest for automated grading.